  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "html": "当年台湾中学<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">地理<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">dì lǐ — geography</span></span>课都像历史课，大陆地理内容都停留在1949年。各省<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">物产<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">wù chǎn — local products</span></span><span class=\\\"vocab\\\">资源<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">zī yuán — natural resources</span></span>、东北九省我们记得一清二楚。“钢都鞍山，煤都抚顺”，我总以为是东北最大的两座城市。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p1.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "2006年的电影《姨妈的后现代生活》里，斯琴高娃<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">扮演<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">bàn yǎn — to play (a role/character)</span></span>的叶如棠，<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">抛夫弃女<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">pāo fū qì nǚ — abandon husband and daughter</span></span>从东北回上海，<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">自称<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">zì chēng — call oneself</span></span>从美国洛杉矶回来，过着她单身而文艺的生活。后来因为伤病入院，不得不联系家属。她十几年不见的<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">粗俗<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">cū sú — vulgar; coarse</span></span>女儿来到医院<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">询问<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">xún wèn — inquire</span></span>，护士本来挺<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">冷漠<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">lěng mò — indifferent; apathetic</span></span>，一听是叶女士女儿，<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">秒变<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">miǎo biàn — change instantly</span></span>热情“回来哒？”赵薇一愣“洛杉矶？<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">俺<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">ǎn — I; me (dialect)</span></span>是鞍山的！”护士马上明白过来，又变得一脸<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">鄙视<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">bǐ shì — despise; look down on</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "电影的最后，叶如棠回到鞍山，在市场<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">支<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">zhī — set up, put up</span></span>起<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">小摊<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">xiǎo tān — street stall</span></span>，面无表情地吃馒头……",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山主城区是当年<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">伪满<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">wěi mǎn — Manchukuo</span></span><span class=\\\"vocab\\\">时期<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">shí qī — period</span></span>常见的大城市<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">规划<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">guī huà — plan</span></span>：车站前有条大道……",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN1p4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "html": "胜利广场周边最引人<span class=\\\"vocab\\\">瞩目<span class=\\\"tooltip\\\">yǐn rén zhǔ mù — attract attention</span></span>的建筑是“焦耐院”……",
